<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="h-full">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <title>Nota de inscripción | <%= institucion %>
    </title>
</head>

<body class="flex flex-col h-full bg-slate-50 font-outfit text-slate-900">
    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-slate-900/95 backdrop-blur-md shadow-lg">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-20">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center">
                    <a href="/" class="flex items-center space-x-3 group">
                        <img src="/images/blanco.png" class="h-10 w-auto transform transition group-hover:scale-105"
                            alt="logo">
                        <div class="hidden md:block h-8 w-px bg-slate-700 mx-4"></div>
                        <span class="text-white font-semibold text-lg tracking-tight hidden md:inline">Solicitud de Mesa
                            de Examen</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <span
                        class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-primary-500/10 text-primary-400 ring-1 ring-inset ring-primary-500/20">
                        v1.0.0
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-grow">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
                <!-- Sidebar Info -->
                <aside class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-8">
                    <!-- Instructions Card -->
                    <div class="card overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="bg-primary-600 px-6 py-4">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white flex items-center">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                        d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                                </svg>
                                Instrucciones
                            </h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Inscripción a Examen</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium mb-4">Exclusivo para alumnos egresados</p>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                                Completa el formulario con tus datos reales. Al finalizar, obtendrás un documento PDF
                                listo para imprimir y presentar en secretaría.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Important Info Card -->
                    <div class="card p-6">
                        <h3
                            class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                            </svg>
                            Información Importante
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-4">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="flex-shrink-0 h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-0.5">•</span>
                                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Las mesas se solicitan de <strong>Abril a
                                        Noviembre</strong>.</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="flex-shrink-0 h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-0.5">•</span>
                                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Presentar la nota antes del <strong>día 10</strong>
                                    de cada mes.</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="flex-shrink-0 h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-0.5">•</span>
                                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">La fecha será confirmada cuando la mesa esté
                                    conformada.</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start p-3 bg-red-50 rounded-xl border border-red-100">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none"
                                    stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                        d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                                </svg>
                                <span class="text-red-700 text-[13px] leading-tight font-medium">Si no te presentas a la
                                    mesa solicitada, se suspende la solicitud por el mes siguiente.</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </aside>

                <!-- Form Section -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-8">
                    <form action="/nota" method="post" class="space-y-8">
                        <!-- Personal Info Card -->
                        <div class="card p-8">
                            <div class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-100 pb-6">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Datos Personales</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">Completa los campos tal como aparecen en tu DNI.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
                                <div class="space-y-2">
                                    <label for="fNombre"
                                        class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 tracking-wide">Nombre</label>
                                    <input type="text" id="fNombre" name="nombre"
                                        class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-500/10 focus:border-primary-500 transition-all outline-none text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400"
                                        placeholder="Ej: Juan Pablo" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-2">
                                    <label for="fApel"
                                        class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 tracking-wide">Apellido</label>
                                    <input type="text" id="fApel" name="apellido"
                                        class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-500/10 focus:border-primary-500 transition-all outline-none text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400"
                                        placeholder="Ej: Pérez" required>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                                <div class="space-y-2 md:col-span-1">
                                    <label for="dni"
                                        class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 tracking-wide">DNI</label>
                                    <input type="number" id="dni" name="dni"
                                        class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-500/10 focus:border-primary-500 transition-all outline-none text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400"
                                        placeholder="Sin puntos" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-2 md:col-span-1">
                                    <label for="egreso" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 tracking-wide">Año
                                        de Egreso</label>
                                    <select name="egreso" id="egreso"
                                        class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-500/10 focus:border-primary-500 transition-all outline-none text-slate-900 cursor-pointer appearance-none">
                                        <option value="" selected disabled>Seleccione año</option>
                                        <% for(let year=(new Date().getFullYear()); year>= 2010; year--) { %>
                                            <option value="<%= year %>">
                                                <%= year %>
                                            </option>
                                            <% } %>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-2 md:col-span-1">
                                    <label for="telefono"
                                        class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 tracking-wide">Teléfono</label>
                                    <input type="number" id="telefono" name="telefono"
                                        class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-500/10 focus:border-primary-500 transition-all outline-none text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400"
                                        placeholder="Cód. área sin 0 y sin 15">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Subjects Card -->
                        <div class="card p-8">
                            <div class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-100 pb-6">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Materias a rendir</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">Puedes rendir hasta 3 materias simultáneamente.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="space-y-6">
                                <div class="relative flex items-center group">
                                    <span
                                        class="absolute left-5 text-slate-400 font-bold group-focus-within:text-primary-600 transition-colors">1.</span>
                                    <input type="text" name="materia1"
                                        class="w-full pl-12 pr-5 py-4 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-500/10 focus:border-primary-500 transition-all outline-none text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400"
                                        placeholder="Nombre completo de la materia">
                                </div>
                                <div class="relative flex items-center group text-slate-400 font-bold">
                                    <span
                                        class="absolute left-5 group-focus-within:text-primary-600 transition-colors">2.</span>
                                    <input type="text" name="materia2"
                                        class="w-full pl-12 pr-5 py-4 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-500/10 focus:border-primary-500 transition-all outline-none text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400"
                                        placeholder="Opcional">
                                </div>
                                <div class="relative flex items-center group text-slate-400 font-bold">
                                    <span
                                        class="absolute left-5 group-focus-within:text-primary-600 transition-colors">3.</span>
                                    <input type="text" name="materia3"
                                        class="w-full pl-12 pr-5 py-4 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-500/10 focus:border-primary-500 transition-all outline-none text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400"
                                        placeholder="Opcional">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 pt-4">
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm flex items-center">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                        d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                                </svg>
                                Proceso de generación seguro
                            </p>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto px-12 py-4 text-lg">
                                Generar Nota PDF
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-white border-t border-slate-200 mt-20">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10">
            <div
                class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 text-center md:text-left">
                <div class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">
                    © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <span class="text-slate-900 font-bold italic tracking-tight">
                            <%= institucion %>
                        </span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-8">
                    <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank"
                        class="text-slate-500 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors flex items-center group">
                        <span class="font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mr-2 opacity-50">developed by</span>
                        <span
                            class="font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">maex.dev</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>